				\begin{document}$${E}_{ff} \sim Z\times {n}_{e}^{2}/[({T}_{e})1/2\times {g}_{ff}\times \nu ]$$\end{document}, where gff is the velocity averaged gaunt factor74, and ν is the spectral bandwidth of the diagnostic.

